### Quick Test Suite - Run these in sequence to see Morgan logs

### 1. GET all movies
GET http://localhost:3000/movies

###

### 2. CREATE a new movie
POST http://localhost:3000/movies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Test Movie",
  "director": "Test Director",
  "year": 2024
}

###

### 3. GET the new movie (use ID from previous response)
GET http://localhost:3000/movies/4

###

### 4. UPDATE the movie
PUT http://localhost:3000/movies/4
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Test Movie",
  "year": 2025
}

###

### 5. FILTER movies by year
GET http://localhost:3000/movies?year=2025

###

### 6. DELETE the movie
DELETE http://localhost:3000/movies/4

###

### 7. Verify deletion (should return 404)
GET http://localhost:3000/movies/4

###

### 8. Test error - invalid year
POST http://localhost:3000/movies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Bad Movie",
  "director": "Bad Director",
  "year": "invalid"
}

###

### 9. Test error - missing fields
POST http://localhost:3000/movies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Incomplete Movie"
}

###

### 10. Test catch-all route
GET http://localhost:3000/nonexistent-route

###
